      "span_text": "The empirical similarity spectra [CITATION_1] for the two sources of turbulent mixing noise, the large (LSS) and fine-scale (FSS) turbulent structures, exhibit a large degree of congruity with the noise from an F-22A Raptor recorded at a near-field sideline array of ground-based microphones for three engine conditions: intermediate (80%), military, and afterburner.",
